1.0 - Old Nomickers don't die...

      Silent players are no longer deregistered, but become Zombies.
      Zombies are initially owned by the bank, but are Auctioned off
      for Indulgences (which effectively go towards paying off that
      Zombie's Blots).
 
      The player who so buys a Zombie, gains its Power of Attorney.
      If the Zombie player returns to the game, its Master is 
      refunded some of eir price.

      ...the just get amended.

1.1 - If a Zombie is not bought, it is deregistered, to prevent lots
      of unwanted Zombies from being Auctioned every week.

      Fixed a bug in the refund rule (forgot to say who was being paid).

      Zombies cannot become Officers, Judges, etc.

